results.name: Fresh Foam Hierro v6 2E Wide 'Light Rogue Wave'
results.story: The New Balance Fresh Foam Hierro v6 2E Wide ‘Light Rogue Wave’ pairs a rugged build with resilient cushioning. The trail running shoe features a bright blue mesh upper strengthened with zonal TPU threads woven into high-wear areas. Toe Protect offers added durability against rocks and other debris found on outdoor trails. The bootie-style upper is mounted on a precision-engineered Fresh Foam midsole, reinforced underfoot by a lugged Vibram rubber outsole.

results.name: Wmns Speedcat LS 'Black White'
results.story: The PUMA women’s Speedcat LS ‘Black White’ delivers a simple two-tone colorway of a low-profile silhouette inspired by F1 racing. The streamlined upper is outfitted in black suede with a tonal T-toe overlay and a contrasting white suede Formstrip. Jumping cat branding lands on the heel tab and lateral toe, while a gold-foil PUMA No. 1 Logo is stamped on the quarter panel. Underfoot, the rubber outsole features a distinctive tire tread and a rounded driver’s heel for added traction.

results.name: Fresh Foam Hierro v6 4E Wide 'Ghost Pepper Habanero'
results.story: The New Balance Fresh Foam Hierro v6 4E Wide ‘Ghost Pepper Habanero’ applies a fiery palette to a trail running shoe that balances comfort and durability. Laser perforations enhance the breathability of the mesh upper, fortified with TPU yarns and Toe Protect technology. The lightweight build is mounted on a full-length Fresh Foam midsole, precision-engineered for soft cushioning and energy return. Underfoot, a solid rubber Vibram outsole is equipped with outdoor lugs for optimal grip.

results.name: Fresh Foam Hierro v6 'Light Rogue Wave'
results.story: The New Balance Fresh Foam Hierro v6 ‘Light Rogue Wave’ combines a tough, trail-ready build with responsive cushioning. The breathable mesh upper incorporates TPU yarns for improved durability and Toe Protect technology to shield against rocks and other debris. A seamless heel counter provides rearfoot support and enhanced stability. The sneaker rides on a full-length Fresh Foam midsole, offering compression and energy return with each step. Underfoot, a high-traction Vibram outsole delivers superior grip in all conditions.

results.name: Flex Runner GS 'Game Royal'
results.story: Developed for big kids, the Nike Flex Runner GS ‘Game Royal’ showcases a gradient blue finish on a versatile slip-on built for play. The stretchy sock-like mesh upper is reinforced with no-sew overlays and a midfoot cage with elastic straps that wrap over the tongue and around the heel. Dual webbing pull tabs provide easy on and off. The vibrant blue and crimson hues up top are offset by a solid white foam sole, featuring flex grooves underfoot for a smooth ride.

results.name: Fresh Foam Hierro v6 2E Wide 'Ghost Pepper Habanero'
results.story: The New Balance Fresh Foam Hierro v6 2E Wide ‘Ghost Pepper Habanero’ delivers a fiery colorway of a trail running shoe designed to withstand punishing terrain. The composition of the engineered mesh upper includes TPU yarns for added durability, while a Toe Protect overlay guards against rocks and other debris. A gusseted tongue and padded collar combine for a comfortable fit. The sneaker rides on a plush Fresh Foam midsole, supported by a lugged Vibram outsole with a heel rudder for added traction.

results.name: D.O.N. Issue #2 'Championship'
results.story: The adidas D.O.N. Issue #2 ‘Championship’ updates Donovan Mitchell’s second signature shoe with a tonal black finish and metallic gold detailing throughout. On the black mesh upper, gold streaks are complemented by a medial-side gold overlay stamped with ‘Championship’ in contrasting black lettering. Additional gilded accents land on branding hits at the tongue and molded heel. Lightweight cushioning arrives via a black Bounce midsole covered in gold speckling.

results.name: adidas ZX 8000 Out There
results.story: The adidas ZX 8000 ‘Out There’ delivers a rugged interpretation of the vintage runner. Breathable black canvas is utilized on the upper, accented with tiger camo detailing and interchangeable hook-and-loop straps that display various city names, years and zip codes. A removable snap-button pocket features the same tiger camo print and a convenient transparent window. The sneaker rides on a lightly speckled EVA midsole, reinforced underfoot by a decoupled gum rubber outsole.

results.name: Air Max Excee PS 'Iron Grey Game Royal'
results.story: Built for little kids, the Nike Air Max Excee PS ‘Iron Grey Game Royal’ highlights vibrant accents on a lifestyle runner inspired by the Air Max 90. The sneaker utilizes a breathable grey mesh upper with tonal leather overlays at the forefoot and heel. Contrast stitching in Volt lines the edges of the grey suede saddle, partially obscured by a royal blue leather Swoosh. The latter hue is repeated on cassette detailing that frames the Volt-colored Max Air unit nestled in the heel.

results.name: Flex Advance TD 'Volt Grey Fog'
results.story: The Nike Flex Advance TD ‘Volt Grey Fog’ offers easy wearability for little feet. The two-tone textile upper is secured with Nike FlyEase technology, comprising an extra-wide opening, dual webbing pull tabs and hook-and-loop straps that crisscross over the vamp for custom fit. The slip-on rests on a cushy white foam sole unit, featuring flex grooves and a pivot circle underfoot. They’re joined by rubber pods under the heel and toe for added durability.

results.name: ASICS Gel-Quantam 90 Coca-Cola
results.story: The Coca-Cola x ASICS Gel Quantum 90 ‘Red’ showcases a bold color scheme in keeping with the iconic beverage brand. Recycled polyester — equivalent to four recycled water bottles’ worth — is incorporated in the crimson knit upper, fortified with a midfoot cage inscribed with the Coca-Cola logo on the lateral side. Lightweight cushioning is provided by a solid white EVA midsole, featuring green-tinged Gel cushioning under the heel for enhanced impact protection.

results.name: Flex Advance PS 'Black White'
results.story: Offered in little kid sizing, the Nike Flex Advance PS ‘Black White’ applies an essential two-tone palette to a versatile slip-on built for everyday wear. Nike FlyEase technology replaces traditional laces with an extra-wide opening, pull tabs at the tongue and heel, and two hook-and-loop straps that crisscross over the vamp. The black textile upper is reinforced with a synthetic toe cap and mounted on a contrasting white foam sole unit. Underfoot, durable rubber is placed in high-wear areas for grippy traction.

results.name: Reebok Question Mid I3 Motorsports
results.story: Giving a nod to biker culture, the Reebok Question Mid ‘I3 Motorsports’ applies a metallic silver finish to the stitched leather toe cap and mudguard. They’re contrasted by black synthetic nubuck construction throughout the upper, equipped with a ghillie lacing system and breathable mesh tongue. Silver embroidery lands on Reebok’s Vector branding and Allen Iverson’s Question logo on the heel tab. The sneaker rides on a lightweight EVA midsole, fitted with visible Hexalite cushioning and reinforced by a translucent rubber outsole.

results.name: Wmns Deviate Nitro Elite 'White Lava Blast'
results.story: The PUMA Deviate Nitro Elite ‘White Lava Blast’ features a lightweight build engineered for speed. An off-white finish is applied to the semi-translucent mono mesh upper, accented with a black and red PUMA Formstrip and reflective silver detailing that wraps around the deconstructed collar. A responsive NITRO ELITE foam midsole is supported by a carbon fiber INNOPLATE that generates improved energy transfer at toe-off. Underfoot, a PUMAGRIP LT rubber outsole is good for lasting multi-surface traction.

results.name: Kyrie Flytrap 4 PS 'Summit White Purple Pulse'
results.story: Crafted for little kids, the Nike Kyrie Flytrap 4 PS ‘Summit White Purple Pulse’ showcases a pristine finish with subtle pastel accents. Elastic laces combine with an adjustable hook-and-loop ankle strap to secure the basketball-inspired mid-top, featuring an upper built with textile and synthetic materials. A mesh tongue enhances the shoe’s breathability, while a fabric-lined padded collar delivers a comfortable fit. The sneaker rides on a full-length foam midsole, supported underfoot by a translucent lavender outsole that extends up the sidewalls for added traction.

results.name: Fresh Foam Hierro v6 'Black Spruce Timberwolf'
results.story: The New Balance Fresh Foam Hierro v6 ‘Black Spruce Timberwolf’ features muted earth tones on a trail running shoe built to handle rugged terrain. TPU yarns are woven into one-piece mesh upper, which is further bolstered with a Toe Protect overlay and synthetic heel counter. Laser perforations and a mesh tongue enhance the shoe’s overall breathability. The lightweight build rests on a Fresh Foam midsole, good for a blend of plush cushioning and responsiveness. Underfoot, a lugged Vibram outsole offers durable traction.

results.name: Fresh Foam Hierro v6 4E Wide 'Light Rogue Wave'
results.story: The New Balance Fresh Foam Hierro v6 4E Wide ‘Light Rogue Wave’ showcases a vibrant blue finish on a trail running shoe built for rough terrain. TPU threads are woven into the mesh upper for added durability, while laser perforations offer increased ventilation. The lightweight build is mounted on a Fresh Foam midsole, good for soft landings and increased energy return. Underfoot, a lugged Vibram rubber outsole ensures grippy traction on or off the trail.

results.name: Gel DS Trainer 26 'Black Pure Silver'
results.story: The ASICS Gel DS Trainer 26 ‘Black Pure Silver’ delivers a neutral colorway of a running shoe made for athletes who want to go fast over shorter distances. The form-fitting engineered knit upper, accented with reflective detailing for added visibility in low-light conditions, sits on a FlyteFoam midsole with Gel cushioning in the heel. Underfoot, ASICS’ Propulsion Trusstic technology generates forward momentum by mirroring the function of the foot’s ligaments.

results.name: Air Max Excee TD 'White Pure Platinum'
results.story: The Nike Air Max Excee TD ‘White Pure Platinum’ introduces classic Air Max style to a new generation of sneaker enthusiasts. Specifically, the Excee takes inspiration from the Air Max 90, highlighted by a breathable white mesh upper with contrasting leather and suede overlays. Additionally, a plush foam midsole is enhanced with an orange-tinged Max Air unit in the heel, contained within grey cassette detailing. Underfoot, the outsole comes complete with flex grooves and a classic waffle tread.

results.name: All Coasts 574 'Brown'
results.story: The New Balance All Coasts 574 ‘Brown’ combines court-inspired details with a versatile low-top silhouette built for everyday wear. The upper is constructed from breathable black mesh with brown suede overlays throughout. Contrasting pops of color arrive via an emerald heel clip and a purple suede overlay that dips below the collar. The streamlined build sits atop a REVlite midsole, made with a lightweight foam compound that delivers lightweight cushioning with each step.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Dainty Mule 'Washed Florals - Storm Wind Pure Silver'
results.story: Releasing as part of a ‘Washed Florals’ pack, the Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star Dainty Mule ‘Storm Wind Pure Silver’ opens up the heel and transforms the low-top into a stylish slip-on. Traditional laces secure the dark brown canvas upper, enlivened with metallic silver binding on the tongue, collar and throat. The sneaker’s interior lining is rendered in a hot pink finish, complemented by watercolor florals on the custom sockliner.

results.name: Air Max 270 TD 'Black Game Royal'
results.story: The Nike Air Max 270 TD ‘Black Game Royal’ confers the sensation of big Air cushioning to a new generation of sneaker lovers. The slip-on makes use of a breathable black mesh upper with no-tie elastic laces an extended webbing pull tab at the heel for easy on and off. Lightweight cushioning arrives via a plush foam midsole with a blue-tinged Max Air heel unit nestled in the heel. Underfoot, flex grooves in the outsole yield added comfort and a smooth ride.

results.name: Gel Cumulus 23 'Reborn Blue'
results.story: The ASICS Gel Cumulus 23 ‘Reborn Blue’ showcases an abstract all-over print throughout the engineered mesh upper, made with 20% recycled materials and featuring targeted areas of enhanced support or breathability. The running shoe is mounted on a lightweight FlyteFoam midsole with ASICS Gel technology in the heel for impact protection. The top layer of the midsole is supplemented with 3D Space Construction, comprising a series of strategically planted pillars that deliver improved compression without sacrificing stability.

results.name: Nike Crater Impact Summit White Green Glow (W)
results.story: The Nike women’s Crater Impact ‘Summit White’ pairs a pastel palette with efficient construction designed to reduce manufacturing waste. The latter is achieved through the application of an embroidered Swoosh and straight-edged overlays on a minimalist mesh upper. Plush cushioning arrives via a lifted Crater foam midsole built with 12% recycled content. Underfoot, the outsole features durable rubber in high-wear areas made with 15% Nike Grind.

results.name: adidas Ultra Boost DNA Lego
results.story: The LEGO x adidas UltraBoost DNA features transparent three-stripes that holds multicolored LEGO plates for a custom mix-and-match aesthetic. The rest of the upper is constructed from white Primeknit that incorporates recycled Parley Ocean Plastic and zero virgin polyester. A metallic silver finish shines on the heel counter and forefoot overlay, while the toe box features a distinctive texture that replicates the look of LEGO bricks. Dual adidas and LEGO branding adorns the tongue and custom sockliner.

results.name: Wmns Classic Nylon SP 'Energy Glow'
results.story: The Reebok women’s Classic Nylon SP ‘Energy Glow’ applies a fluorescent finish to a modernized take on the 1984 original. Stretch nylon is utilized on the upper, fortified with no-sew skins and a midfoot and heel overlay made with synthetic suede. The airy build is mounted on a plush EVA midsole, which works in tandem with a removable EVA sockliner for an ultra-cushioned ride. Underfoot, gum rubber is placed in high-wear areas for optimal grip.

results.name: Daybreak-Type 'Black White'
results.story: The Nike Daybreak-Type ‘Black White’ delivers a simplistic two-tone edition of the lifestyle runner modeled after the 1979 original. The deconstructed upper is crafted from semi-translucent black mesh with forefoot overlays in tonal synthetic suede. A molded heel counter delivers structural support and rearfoot stability. Across the heel tab, N. 354 branding gives the nod to Nike’s concept-driven line. A waffle-tread rubber outsole adds classic heritage style.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Low 'Color Espadrille - Pink Quartz'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star Low ‘Pink Quartz’ reinterprets the classic sneaker as a summer-ready espadrille. The standard rubber midsole is elevated and covered in braided textile, while the canvas upper is updated with a soft pastel hue and frayed detailing. Chrome eyelets and a Converse All Star tongue tag maintain the classic Chuck Taylor look and feel. Underfoot, a traditional diamond-tread rubber outsole delivers reliable grip.

results.name: Team Hustle D10 PS 'University Red'
results.story: Built for little kids, the Nike Team Hustle D10 PS ‘University Red’ dresses the basketball-inspired sneaker in an essential two-tone color scheme. The crimson mesh upper is accented with contrasting black hits on the Swoosh, tongue and elastic laces. The latter works in concert with an adjustable hook-and-loop ankle strap to deliver a custom fit. Soft cushioning arrives via a full-length foam midsole, supported by a durable rubber outsole marked with a large ‘X’ — a nod to the 10th edition of the Hustle D line.

results.name: Nike Crater Impact Light Bone Crimson
results.story: The Nike Crater Impact ‘Light Bone Black’ continues the brand’s sustainability efforts with a lightweight build that incorporates 25% recycled content by weight. The figure is derived through the inclusion of recycled polyester laces, a speckled Crater foam midsole and a rubber outsole made in part with Nike Grind. Additionally, the minimalist mesh upper is the product of efficient construction methods, highlighted by embroidered accents and straight-edged overlays.

results.name: adidas Ultra Boost DNA 1.0 ZX 6000
results.story: The adidas UltraBoost 1.0 DNA ‘ZX 6000’ combines a retro running aesthetic with a contemporary performance build. While the Primeknit upper features woven construction modeled after the original UltraBoost from 2015, the familiar color scheme recalls the OG ZX 6000 that debuted in 1989 alongside adidas’ iconic Torsion system. Adding to the sneaker’s vintage look are a suede forefoot overlay and an off-white finish on the Boost midsole. Underfoot, the Stretchweb outsole uses Continental rubber for grippy traction.

results.name: Mr. Doodle x Wmns Oslo Maja 'Ultramarine American Beauty'
results.story: Inspired by the British artist’s ‘one line-drawings,’ the Mr. Doodle x PUMA women’s Oslo Maja ‘Ultramarine American Beauty’ features an all-over graphic formed with one continuous line. The doodle-like illustration covers a canvas upper in mismatched blue and red finishes. Asymmetric color blocking continues on the chenille Formstrip, rendered in orange and yellow on the lateral and medial side. Mr. Doodle branding appears on the tongue tag, while his illustrated characters adorn each heel tab. A platform EVA midsole anchors the low-top.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Platform High 'Washed Florals - Egret'
results.story: Launching as part of a ‘Washed Florals’ collection, the Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star Platform High ‘Egret’ updates the iconic sneaker with elevated tooling and spring-ready details. An off-white finish is applied to the recycled poly-canvas upper, featuring a washed-out floral print on the binding that lines the collar and throat. The faded florals are repeated on the circular Chuck Taylor patch that adorns medial ankle. A raised platform midsole packs soft EVA cushioning for a improved comfort.

results.name: Mr. Doodle x Wmns Cruise Rider 'Eggnog Ultramarine'
results.story: The Mr. Doodle x PUMA women’s Cruise Rider ‘Eggnog Ultramarine’ draws inspiration from the British artist’s ‘one-line drawings,’ featuring illustrations formed with one long continuous line. The sneaker makes use of a cream-colored textile upper with contrasting red suede overlays at the toe and heel. On the lateral side, a bird doodle is embroidered atop a blue leather Formstrip. Mr. Doodle branding makes its way to the woven tongue tag and exaggerated foam midsole.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Low 'Color Espadrille - Banana Cake'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star Low ‘Banana Cake’ transforms the classic silhouette into a summer-ready espadrille, highlighted by an EVA midsole with braided-textile sidewalls. Up top, the yellow canvas build is decorated with frayed foxing that enhances the shoe’s breezy aesthetic. Additional details include a tonal canvas toe cap, chrome eyelets and a standard Converse All Star tag atop the tongue. A traditional Chuck Taylor outsole in brown rubber provides durable traction.

results.name: Court Legacy TD 'Midnight Navy'
results.story: The Nike Court Legacy TD ‘Midnight Navy’ brings classic tennis style to growing feet. The low-top’s navy leather upper is accented with a white retro Swoosh and a matching white Nike wordmark on the heel tab. Elastic no-tie laces combine with an adjustable hook-and-loop ankle strap to deliver a secure, custom fit. Underfoot, a durable gum rubber outsole features a classic herringbone traction pattern for superior grip.

results.name: Question Mid Toddler 'I3 Motorsports'
results.story: Inspired by ATVs and dirt bikes, the Reebok Question Mid Toddler ‘I3 Motorsports’ delivers a miniature version of Allen Iverson’s debut signature shoe. The sneaker makes use of a black leather upper with embroidered branding hits on the tongue, quarter panel and heel. A contrasting metallic silver finish shines on the mudguard and signature toe cap. Accented with faux Hexalite detailing, the soft foam midsole is supported by a smoky translucent outsole.

results.name: Wmns EvoRide 2 'Black White'
results.story: The ASICS women’s EvoRide 2 ‘Black White’ presents an elemental two-tone colorway of a lightweight silhouette built for daily runs. The black engineered mesh upper is made with 20% recycled materials and designed to keep feet cool. The supportive feel of the FlyteFoam midsole is enhanced with GuideSole technology, featuring pronounced toe-spring that generates forward propulsion and increased efficiency. Underfoot, the Aharplus outsole places durable rubber in high-wear areas for optimal grip.

results.name: adidas Ultra Boost DNA 1.0 Aqua ZX 8000
results.story: The adidas UltraBoost 1.0 DNA ‘ZX 8000’ replicates the look of the iconic running shoe from 1988, highlighted by an OG-inspired color scheme that blends a light teal base with contrasting yellow and violet accents. The breathable Primeknit upper is modeled after the original UltrBoost from 2015 and fortified with a suede forefoot overlay that nods to the ZX 8000. Responsive cushioning comes courtesy of an aqua-colored Boost midsole, supported by adidas’ Torsion bar and a Stretchweb Continental rubber outsole.

results.name: Question Mid Big Kid 'I3 Motorsports'
results.story: The Reebok Question Mid Big Kid ‘I3 Motorsports’ carries an upper that combines matte black synthetic leather with shiny metallic silver accents, a dynamic that mirrors the two-tone finish commonly featured on ATVs and dirt bikes. Allen Iverson’s Question logo is embroidered on the heel tab, complementing Reebok Vector branding on the quarter panel and tongue, the latter featuring mesh construction for enhanced airflow. The sneaker rests on a foam midsole with sculpted sidewalls that mimic the Hexalite cushioning of the original.

results.name: adidas Ultra Boost DNA 1.0 ZX 9000
results.story: The adidas UltraBoost 1.0 DNA ‘ZX 9000’ features a familiar design steeped in the brand’s running heritage. In addition to a Primeknit upper that uses the same woven construction as the original UltraBoost from 2015, the vibrant palette gives the nod to the OG ZX 9000. Bright aqua coloring up top is countered by a full-length Boost midsole, rendered in an off-white finish for a vintage aesthetic. Underfoot, a Stretchweb Continental rubber outsole delivers grippy traction.

results.name: Wmns Crater Impact 'Football Grey'
results.story: The Nike women’s Crater Impact ‘Football Grey’ highlights neon accents on a tracik-inspired silhouette that channels the brand’s sustainability efforts. 100% recycled polyester laces secure a light grey mesh upper, accented with an embroidered Swoosh and straight-edged overlays that yield efficient manufacturing and scrap waste reduction. 12% recycled content makes up the composition of the speckled Crater foam midsole, supported underfoot by durable rubber made in part with Nike Grind.

results.name: Converse Chuck Taylor All-Star 70 Kim Jones Black
results.story: The Kim Jones x Converse Chuck 70 High ‘Black’ offers the renowned fashion designer’s modern interpretation of the foundational sneaker. The high-top makes use of a 12oz black canvas upper, reinforced with a transparent TPU cage that integrates speed hooks into the lacing system. Wavy off-white rubber foxing enhances the protective, utilitarian aesthetic. Underfoot, the rubber outsole features an updated diamond-grid tread for enhanced traction. Exterior branding includes a traditional All Star ankle patch and ‘Kim Jones’ stamped on the tongue.

results.name: Question Mid Little Kid 'I3 Motorsports'
results.story: The Reebok Question Mid Little Kid ‘I3 Motorsports’ features a two-tone finish inspired by ATVs and dirt bikes, which frequently use a high-contrast matte finish with gloss detailing. An integrated lacing system secures an upper built with black synthetic leather. Reebok Vector branding is embroidered on the quarter panel and tongue, featuring open mesh construction for improved breathability. A polished metallic silver finish distinguishes the mudguard and toe cap. Underfoot, a smoky rubber outsole provides durable traction.

results.name: Team Hustle D10 FlyEase PS 'Black Metallic Silver'
results.story: Built for little kids, the Nike Team Hustle D10 FlyEase PS ‘Black Metallic Silver’ applies an essential two-tone palette to a basketball-inspired mid-top. The black mesh upper is secured with elastic laces and a hook-and-loop strap connected to a wraparound heel zipper, which opens up and allows feet to easily slip in or out. On the lateral side, an oversized metallic silver Swoosh dips below the cushy foam midsole. A durable rubber outsole is marked with a large ‘X,’ marking the 10th installment of the Team Hustle D series.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Dainty Mule 'Washed Florals - Egret Light Gold'
results.story: Drawn from the ‘Washed Florals’ collection, the Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star Dainty Mule ‘Egret Light Gold’ converts the sneaker icon into a convenient slip-on. An off-white canvas upper is trimmed in metallic bronze and secured with traditional lace closure. Converse branding lands on the Ortholite sockliner, featuring a washed-out pink and green floral print. Underfoot, a standard Chuck Taylor rubber outsole comes complete with a familiar diamond traction pattern.

results.name: Team Hustle D10 FlyEase GS 'Black White Metallic Gold'
Wmns Gel Cumulus 23 'Carrier Grey Light Blue'
results.story: The ASICS women’s Gel Cumulus 23 ‘Carrier Grey Light Blue’ features dual-layer mesh construction that yields an intricate all-over design throughout the seamless upper. Made with 20% recycled content, the lightweight build is secured with flat laces that incorporate reflective threads for increased visibility in low-light conditions. Lightweight cushioning is provided by a FlyteFoam midsole with ASICS Gel cushioning in the heel for enhanced impact protection.

results.name: Converse Chuck Taylor All-Star 70 Kim Jones Natural
results.story: Launching as part of a larger collection with the prolific menswear designer, the Kim Jones x Converse Chuck 70 High ‘Black’ updates the sneaker icon with a functional design that blends old and new. A semi-translucent TPU cage reinforces the 12oz canvas upper, complete with speed hooks that augment the conventional lacing system. Wavy rubber foxing offers enhanced protection while adding a modern twist to the sneaker’s straightforward lines. Kim Jones branding adorns each tongue and the sockliner of the left shoe.

results.name: Wmns Crater Impact 'Summit White Grey Fog'
results.story: The Nike women’s Crater Impact ‘Summit White Grey Fog’ highlights isolated pops of color on a track-inspired silhouette made with sustainability in mind. Speckled detailing on the bulky midsole indicates Crater Foam, composed of a blend of recycled Nike Grind and standard foam materials. Up top, the off-white mesh build is enlivened with orange zigzag stitching and a webbing pull tab in the same vibrant hue. An embroidered Swoosh and straight-edged overlays contribute to the sneaker’s efficient build.

results.name: Chuck Taylor All Star Low 'Stars & Stripes'
results.story: The Converse Chuck Taylor All Star Low ‘Stars & Stripes’ delivers a patriotic colorway of the vintage silhouette. The low-top carries a crisp white canvas upper with mismatched detailing: the left shoe features star-covered navy laces and a tongue bedecked in red and white stripes, while the right shoe features starry red laces and a navy tongue arrayed with white stars. The sneaker is finished with standard Chuck Taylor tooling, including a brown rubber outsole with a traditional diamond tread.

results.name: Air Max 270 PS 'Light Smoke Grey Crimson'
results.colorway: Light Smoke Grey/Dark Smoke Grey/Bright Crimson/White
results.story: Crafted for little kids, the Nike Air Max 270 PS ‘Light Smoke Grey Crimson’ spotlights the sneaker’s buoyant cushioning technology. Nestled under the heel, the large-volume Max Air unit is tinted in a bright red hue, matching the glossy TPU heel counter that reinforces the grey mesh upper. An integrated lacing system works in tandem with a stretchy neoprene bootie to deliver a snug, comfortable fit. Heritage-style branding on the exaggerated tongue gives the nod to the classic Air Max 180 from 1991.

results.name: Y-3 Forum Hi OG 'Triple Black'
results.story: The adidas Y-3 Forum Hi OG ‘Triple Black’ delivers Yohji Yamamoto’s fashion-forward take on the retro hoops shoe. A stealthy monochromatic finish is executed on the all-leather upper, secured with an updated ankle strap and zippered detailing that wraps around the heel and extends down the lateral midfoot. The high-top is mounted on a matching black rubber cupsole modeled after the original Forum, complete with a medial-side EVA wedge covered in Dillinger webbing.

Cali Sport Jr 'Fireworks - White Sun Kissed Coral'
Future Z 3.1 FG AG 'White Red Blast'
